## Task #1: Average of Stream

You are given a stream of numbers, `@N`.

Write a script to print the average of the stream at every point.

***

## Solution:

```perl
use strict;
use warnings;
sub moving_average{
    my $n = 0;
    my $sum = 0;
    {
        $n += 1;
        $sum += shift;
        print $sum / $n;
        print ", " if @_;
        redo if @_;
    }
    print "\n";
}

